OL,4,Chospitalised after home exploded
OL,6,FA family of four, including children
OL,7,Faged two and five, have been
OL,8,Fhospitalised after their house
OL,9,Fexploded in Jersey.
OL,11,FThe two adults remain at St Helier's
OL,12,FGeneral Hospital in stable condition
OL,13,Fwith non-life-threatening or life-
OL,14,Fchanging injuries.
OL,16,FBoth children are unharmed and being
OL,17,Fsupported.
OL,19,FResidents close to the incident have
OL,20,Ftold ITV News that their properties
OL,21,Fshook with the force of the explosion.
