OL,6,FSt Saviour Constable Kevin Lewis
OL,7,Fconfirmed a "significant explosion
OL,8,Foccurred near the Merton Hotel in St
OL,9,FSaviour" and called it a "critical
OL,10,Fincident".
OL,12,FEmergency services had declared a
OL,13,Fmajor incident but this has now been
OL,14,Fstood down as they move to the
OL,15,Frecovery phase.
OL,17,FPolice were called to an unexplained
OL,18,Fexplosion at a property in Le Mont
OL,19,FPinel in St Saviour just before 11pm
OL,20,Fon Wednesday night (26 June).
