OL,6,FA total of 19 residents were evacuated
OL,7,Ffrom their homes as a precaution and
OL,8,Fmoved into temporary accommodation.
OL,10,FIsland Energy, the mains gas supplier,
OL,11,Fand Jersey Electricity also attended.
OL,13,FOne resident who lives 20 metres away
OL,14,Ffrom the house did not want to be
OL,15,Fnamed but says: "I was lying in bed
OL,16,Fand it sounded like someone had driven
OL,17,Finto the side of my bedroom. The bang
OL,18,Fis like something I can't even
OL,19,Fdescribe.
