OL,6,F"When I came out, I could just hear
OL,7,Fsomeone saying, 'Call an ambulance and
OL,8,Fthe fire brigade' so I phoned them.
OL,9,FThen I looked up and saw all the wall
OL,10,Fwas blown out.
OL,12,F"I just felt sick, I could see the
OL,13,Fbunkbeds."
OL,15,FAnother neighbour, Karen Basile, adds:
OL,16,F"I was sitting on my bed and there was
OL,17,Fan enormous bang which shook the whole
OL,18,Fhouse, it woke everybody up.
