OL,6,F"The fire service moved everybody back
OL,7,Fand within seconds of them clearing
OL,8,Fthat area, more of the house fell.
OL,10,F"At one point I heard the person in
OL,11,Fcharge say, 'I want everybody out
OL,12,Falive' so it was obviously a very
OL,13,Fdangerous situation."
OL,15,FThe surrounding area is closed to the
OL,16,Fpublic as the States of Jersey Police
OL,17,Fremain on the scene but school traffic
OL,18,Fis not expected to be affected - Mont
OL,19,FMillais is open.
