OL,6,FThe cause of the explosion is
OL,7,Fcurrently unknown.
OL,9,FEngineers will attend the home that
OL,10,Fwas badly damaged and three
OL,11,Fneighbouring properties to assess
OL,12,Ftheir structural integrity before
OL,13,Finvestigations can begin.
OL,15,FJersey's Chief Minister, Deputy Lyndon
OL,16,FFarnham, says: "Our thoughts are with
OL,17,Fthe family affected and those who have
OL,18,Fbeen displaced as a result. The
OL,19,FGovernment is providing ongoing
OL,20,Fsupport to those families."
